tasks.instruction:
The user is getting an error when trying to access the FleetXchange platform preview. From the screenshot provided, there appears to be a build or runtime error preventing the application from loading properly.

Please investigate and fix this issue immediately:

1. Check the current build status and resolve any build errors
2. Verify that all import paths are correct and files exist
3. Test the application routing to ensure the root path "/" works correctly
4. Check for any console errors or missing dependencies
5. Ensure all components are properly exported and imported
6. Fix any TypeScript errors or missing type definitions
7. Test that the login page displays properly when accessing the preview
8. Make sure the improved top navigation layout works correctly

The user needs to be able to access the FleetXchange platform with the top navigation layout. Debug and resolve whatever is preventing the preview from working. Run comprehensive tests and fix any errors that appear.
